{"type":"message","id":"30e43e88","parentId":"fee1f92f","timestamp":"2026-04-14T21:46:49.878Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sessions_list returned empty, which is strange. Let me also check if the cron sessions are still running. The heartbeat state shows some cron sessions but the current sessions_list shows nothing. This could be because the cron sessions are internal and not visible via sessions_list.\n\nLet me check more carefully. The heartbeat state shows:\n- cron:ed2d0b5d — running (5p QLHV monitor)\n- cron:e7885813 — running (Agent Status to Lead)\n- cron:6f3323ef — done (DTLX 5p Monitor)\n\nBut sessions_list shows 0 sessions. This is likely because cron sessions are managed internally and may not show up in sessions_list. \n\nThe cron monitor itself ran and completed, but the sessions it's tracking might be internal or background processes. The key question is whether anything meaningful has actually changed in the system since the last heartbeat.","thinkingSignature":"fd8f8c6268d0a1c0e1474678aa5a85b97f16415a72a0c56b37b70066aaed3e4d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s4j2so6lkvh3_1","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list","includeDisabled":true}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":379,"output":219,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":433,"totalTokens":14975,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776203204505,"responseId":"062de8c5362c1c78d8590e1249356366"}}
{"type":"message","id":"21817ba9","parentId":"30e43e88","timestamp":"2026-04-14T21:46:50.005Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_s4j2so6lkvh3_1","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\",\n      \"agentId\": \"master-orchestrator\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"name\": \"5p Progress Report — AHV DTLX/QLHV\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775986516041,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1776202927611,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 300000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1775986440000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) ecosystem.\\n\\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\\n\\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\\n\\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, task started/completed, blocker appeared), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\\n\\nFormat:\\n🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\\n\\nChanges detected:\\n• [list of actual changes]\\n\\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\\n• Active sessions: N\\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\n\\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"-5163901258\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1776203164454,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1776202864454,\n        \"lastRunS