ces, and likely legacy carryovers.\\n- Be evidence-based from files only.\\n\\nDeliverables to write in your workspace docs:\\n1) ROUTE_MAP_AHV_DRIVING.md\\n2) HANDOVER.md\\n\\nRequired output structure for ROUTE_MAP_AHV_DRIVING.md:\\n- Executive summary\\n- Entry flow\\n- Route/module inventory table\\n- Business-domain grouping\\n- Naming inconsistencies / legacy drift\\n- Unknowns / needs runtime confirmation\\n- Recommended next inspection targets\\n\\nUse concise markdown tables where possible. No filler.\",\n        \"model\": \"sonnet\",\n        \"thinking\": \"medium\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 1800\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1775865390009,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 169731,\n        \"lastError\": \"Delivering to Telegram requires target <chatId>\",\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 14,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 14,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","agentId":"master-orchestrator","sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","name":"5p Progress Report — AHV DTLX/QLHV","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1775986516041,"updatedAtMs":1776202927611,"schedule":{"kind":"every","everyMs":300000,"anchorMs":1775986440000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent f