y\n  - logging consistency audit against current logger convention\n  - validation/error-handling consistency\n  - performance hotspot summary\n  - security/sensitive-data handling observations\n  - top BE defects/risk list with severity\n- System summary:\n  - end-to-end contract drift\n  - highest-risk modules\n  - release-blocker candidates\n  - recommended remediation order\n- API unused-fields audit:\n  - follow existing QA brief strictly\n  - report only, conservative evidence standard\n\nConstraints:\n- No fixes.\n- No code edits.\n- Be brutally concrete, evidence-based, and cite file paths.\n- If uncertain, label uncertainty explicitly.\n- Focus on the currently implemented FE/BE, not hypothetical future scope.\n\nOutput quality bar:\n- concise but hard-hitting\n- tables where useful\n- explicit severity labels: Critical / High / Medium / Low\n- final HANDOVER must summarize status, audited modules, key findings, and what still needs runtime verification.\n\nWhen finished, write all deliverables and report completion succinctly.","model":"sonnet","thinking":"medium","timeoutSeconds":0,"lightContext":true},"delivery":{"mode":"announce"},"state":{"lastRunAtMs":1775831304228,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":573976,"lastError":"Delivering to Telegram requires target <chatId>","lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":1}},{"id":"f1781cad-6f99-46c6-b31c-0986aac04518","agentId":"researcher","sessionKey":"agent:team-orchestrator:cron:ad7f8cd3-5b36-4054-95ef-bee3f6bc4753","name":"ahv-driving-backend-phase1-brainstorm","description":"Phase 1 brainstorming for AHV driving backend migration","enabled":false,"deleteAfterRun":true,"createdAtMs":1775896055582,"updatedAtMs":1775896236201,"schedule":{"kind":"at","at":"2026-04-11T08:28:00.000Z"},"sessionTarget":"session:ahv-driving-backend-research-phase1","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"Project root is locked to `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-s